abstract: Trading hoodies at the home office for hard pants, we take a snapshot of the finance bros in their native habitat.
snippet: Trading hoodies at the home office for hard pants, we take a snapshot of the finance bros in their native habitat.
lead_paragraph: Reporting here from the Hot Tub Time Machine, dial set to 2010. Business analysts and those with even a passing interest in men’s wear will remember that as the year when Suit Supply became a worldwide phenomenon. It was also when, for the first time, novel technology enabled men to customize their own suits online without having to submit to pesky nuisances like tailors or the bother of going into a store.

main: How Should a Business Bro Dress?
